ly designed website solution for their industry.  Easily add your own custom logo, and easily customize the look and feel with dozens of google fonts to choose from.</p>\n<p>To view a full website demo or screenshots and features, click through to the <a href="http://www.totalbounty.com/shop/mkt/item/blush-salon-wordpress-theme">Blush Salon WordPress Theme</a> product page.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.totalbounty.com/shop/mkt/item/blush-salon-wordpress-theme"><img src="http://www.totalbounty.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/flyover2.jpg" alt="Blush Salon WordPress theme" title="Blush Salon WordPress theme" width="590" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1157" /></a></p>\n<h2>Cosmopolitan Beauty Theme</h2>\n<p>Cosmopolitan is the amazing salon theme for WordPress with a sophisticated look and feel.  This website design would be perfect for health spas, tanning or nail salons, clothing designers, fashion coordinators, personal stylists, hair stylists &#8211; or anyone in the beauty and fashion industries.</p>\n<p>To walk through the theme features please visit <a href="http://www.totalbounty.com/shop/mkt/item/cosmopolitan-salon-spa-theme">The Cosmopolitan WordPress Theme</a> product page.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.totalbounty.com/shop/mkt/item/cosmopolitan-salon-spa-theme"><img src="http://www.totalbounty.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/flyover1.jpg" alt="The Cosmopolitan WordPress theme" title="The Cosmopolitan WordPress theme" width="590" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1156" /></a></p>\n<p>All 3 of these new WordPress beauty themes are now available for purchase and download &#8211; and all come with incredibly detailed and easy to understand user manuals and personal email support.  Visit the Total Bounty Marketplace today to find just the website theme to suit your needs!</p>\n<div class="aizattos_related_posts"><span class="aizattos_related_posts_header" >Related Posts</span><ul><li><span class="aizattos_related_posts_title"><a href=